official_title: A Prospective Series of IVF Cases Utilizing in Vitro Maturation (IVM) With Low Cost Priming, Enhanced Oocyte Recovery, and Delayed Embryo Transfer Using a Subsequent Frozen Embryo Transfer Cycle
inclusion_criteria:
* PCO pattern with > 25 antral follicles
* AMH > 3.5
Healthy volunteers allowed
Must be FEMALE
Must have minimum age of 18 Years
Must have maximum age of 38 Years
exclusion_criteria:
* BMI > 35
* body morphology making transvaginal retrieval difficult or impossible
* complicating medical condition making pregnancy or IVF relatively contra-indicated
